an class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>클로저가 실행되는 순간에 <code>self</code>의 초기화가 완료됐는지를 보장할 수 없기 때문에 컴파일 에러가 발생한다.<br>\n<code>self</code>가 포함된 코드는 다시 <code>viewDidLoad()</code>로 내려야될까?</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>lazy var를 이용한 지연 초기화</h2>\n<p>다행히 <code>lazy var</code>라는 선택지가 있다.<br>\n<code>let dummyButton</code>을 <code>lazy var dummyButton</code>으로 바꿔주자.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container github-light-theme grvsc-ps-t4tStz\" data-language=\"swift\" data-index=\"3\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">import</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-10 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">UIKit</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">class</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-10 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">ViewController</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">: UIViewController {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">    </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">let</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> buttonColor </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">=</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> UIColor.green</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">    </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">lazy</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">var</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> dummyButton</span><span class=\"grvs